Order for Prior Year Tax Products 
(Limited to the 5 Prior Years)  
These and other Prior Year Products are available online. 
Go to https://www.irs.gov/prior-year-forms-and-instructions
Instructions for Completing Form 6112
1 - 5. Enter name and mailing address for order. 
6. Check “Inst.” box if you need the tax form instructions. 
7. Enter the quantity in the box corresponding to the desired Form Number and Tax Year. Shaded boxes indicate forms not available 
for that Tax Year.  
8. You may write in additional forms. Check “Inst.” box to order the form instructions.
